National Seminar on Immortal Feats of Kim Jong Il
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, June 10 (KCNA) -- A national seminar on the immortal feats performed by leader Kim Jong Il in accomplishing the Juche-based cause of party building took place at the People's Palace of Culture on Thursday.
 Present there were Choe Thae Bok and Jong Ha Chol, secretaries of the Central Committee of the Workers' Party of Korea. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Those who presented papers at the seminar said the 40-year-long history in which Kim Jong Il has led the WPK is a glorious history of revolutionary leadership in which he has brought about an epochal turn in strengthening and developing the WPK by successfully settling the matters of decisive significance in building a revolutionary party of Juche type. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Kim Jong Il set out long ago the philosophical principle that the revolutionary idea of the leader means the guiding idea of the party and has performed immortal feats in imbuing the whole party with the revolutionary idea of the leader, the Juche-based idea of the red flag, they noted, and went on: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
The Juche-based theory of party building gave a unique exposition of the essence and mission of the party with the leader as supreme brain that it is a political organization performing a pivotal function in uniting the popular masses around the leader and organizing and mobilizing them to realize the cause of the leader and a servant for the people as it takes care of their destiny in a responsible manner. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 A particular mention should made of the fact that he put forward the theory of party building reflecting the rapidly changing situation in the last decade of the 20th century and the requirements of a new era of the Juche revolution, the Songun era, and has successfully applied it, developing the WPK into the most revolutionary and militant party. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The hardcore in the socio-political foundation of the party leading the revolutionary cause of Songun should be carried out by the army and the socio-political foundation should, in essence, become the most solid and powerful single-hearted unity of the army and the people characterized by their perfect unity in thinking and fighting spirit based on the revolutionary soldier spirit. This is the original idea on social and class foundation of a revolutionary party in the Songun era expounded by him from a new angle.

Pyongsu J-V Company Ltd. Commissioned
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, June 10 (KCNA) -- The Pyongsu J-V Company Ltd., a new pharmaceutical producer, was commissioned with due ceremony at the Pyongyang Pharmaceutical Factory on June 9.
  Present at the ceremony were Minister of Foreign Trade Rim Kyong Man, Vice-Minister of Public Health Jon Hyon Phung, Chairman of the DPRK Committee for the Promotion of Economic Cooperation with Foreign Countries Paek Hyon Bong, officials of the company, officials concerned and employees of the factory. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Attending it were Peter Zuellig, chief executive of the Interpacific of Switzerland, and his party, Eckhard Hoffmann, managing director of the company, Felix Abt, managing director of the Interpacific Holding in the DPRK, foreign diplomatic envoys and embassy officials here, representatives and staff members of international organizations and Samlee Plianbangchang, director of the Regional Office for Southeast Asia of the World Health Organization, and his party on a visit to the DPRK and other foreigners. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
   Eckhard Hoffmann in a report referred to the construction of a modern j-v company and extended thanks to the staff members of the company and builders for the great efforts made to construct it. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 He hoped that the company would be successfully operated by concerted efforts in the future. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Peter Zuellig and Ju Jong Ho, manager of the factory, made congratulatory speeches. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The participants went round its production processes after the cutting of the red cloth seen hanging in front of the building of the company.

Economic and Commercial Councilors Corps Visits Revolutionary Site
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, June 10 (KCNA) -- The Economic and Commercial Councilors Corps in Pyongyang on June 9 visited the revolutionary site on Mt. Jang on the occasion of the 40th anniversary of leader Kim Jong Il's start of work at the Central Committee of the Workers' Party of Korea.
 They were told that Kim Jong Il wisely guided students and soldiers, himself doing work, when he took part in the expansion project of the Wasan-dong-Ryongsong road, true to President Kim Il Sung's far-reaching plan for building Pyongyang, and matured Juche-based military theory and tactics in the period of his revolutionary activities at Kim Il Sung University. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
They went round the historical buildings and remains with deep interest. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
Evelio Duenas Ponce, commercial councilor of the Cuban embassy who is doyen of the corps, wrote in the visitor's book that he was pleased to visit the historic place where       Kim Jong Il took warm care of the life of students and soldiers.

Seminar of Party Cadre Training Institutions Held
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, June 10 (KCNA) -- A seminar of party cadre training institutions was held at Kim Il Sung Higher Party School on June 9 to mark the 40th anniversary of leader Kim Jong Il's start of work at the Central Committee of the Workers' Party of Korea.
 The speakers said his start of work at the WPK Central Committee in June Juche 53 (1964) was a historic event which opened a new epochal phase in accomplishing the cause of the Korean revolution and the cause of party building started in Mt. Paektu. They profoundly explained his immortal revolutionary feats in leading the WPK along an ever-victorious road. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 With a review of the 100 year-long history of working class ideas and scientific penetration into the limitations of the preceding theories long ago, he became the first in history to put forward the original theory of party building the core of which is the issue of the position and role of the leader and gave flawless answers to all the theoretical and practical questions arising in party building and activities on the basis of the idea of believing in the people as in Heaven, they noted. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 They underscored the immortal leadership exploits of Kim Jong Il in strengthening and developing the WPK into ranks of harmonious whole in which all the party members are united close around the leader as passionate comrades and pure-hearted comrades, steel-like ranks united as one on the basis of loyalty to the leader and a tested veteran party with invincible leadership ability. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Under the wise leadership of Kim Jong Il who has established the Korean-style original work system and method in the whole Party and made sure that the Party work was done in conformity with the demand and aspiration of the masses and their emotion and sentiments, the WPK has been strengthened and developed into a powerful party with the most revolutionary and popular leadership art, they stressed. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 They called upon all the party cadre training institutions to constantly improve educational work, true to his intention, and train more and better officials who would shoulder the revolutionary cause of Juche, thus making tangible contributions to building a great prosperous powerful socialist nation. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Present at the seminar was Kim Kuk Thae, secretary of the WPK Central Committee.

Stone Painting
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, June 10 (KCNA) -- Stone paintings drew viewers' interests at the 7th Pyongyang International Trade Fair held in the Democratic People's Republic of Korea.
 The stone painting is drawn by coloring natural granites and marbles through the infiltration of natural pigments. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The stone paintings can be preserved long for their unchangeable color and chemical stability. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The concentration of infiltrated liquid is 10-15 percent and the color-setting temperature 130-250 degrees centigrade. And the depth of color infiltration is 5 to 10mm, 30 to 35mm at maximum. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Several colored granite samples were exposed to sunlight comparable to that of 70 years in outdoor conditions and 100 to 120 degrees centigrade temperature for 12 hours and were put into water for 60 days and 20 percent sulphuric acid, hydrochloric acid and caustic soda solutions for eight hours. The test result showed there was no change in color. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The Korean International Exhibition and Trade Corporation has exported stone landscape paintings to other Asian countries.

Pharmacopoeia Off Press
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, June 10(KCNA) -- The Pharmacopoeia Compilation Committee of the Democratic People's Republic of Korea has published "Pharmacopoeia of the Democratic People's Republic of Korea"(sixth edition).
 It consists of part one (Koryo Medicine), part two (Modern Medicine) and appendix. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 It gives 1,417 kinds of medicines, 156 of which are new entries. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Part one deals with Koryo medicines and their manufature, biological medicines, universal method of test and effects, usage and dosage of Koryo medicines. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Given in part two are ingredients, indication and effects of 556 modern medicines and their dosage for adults. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The appendix includes classic prescriptions-- ingredients, effects, indication and usage. They are extracts from Tonguibogam and other medical classics.

Kim Jong Il Inspects KPA Unit
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, June 10 (KCNA) -- Supreme Commander of the Korean People's Army Kim Jong Il, general secretary of the Workers' Party of Korea and chairman of the DPRK National Defence Commission, inspected KPA unit 769 honored with the title of O Jung Hup-led 7th Regiment.
 He looked round the room devoted to the history of the unit. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 He highly praised the exploits performed by the unit, noting that the unit honored with the glorious "Kim Il Sung Order" and the titles of Kum Song Lifeguard and O Jung Hup-led 7th Regiment is a unit with a long tradition as it has taken the lead in upholding the Songun leadership of the WPK by displaying popular heroism in the defence of the country and in the socialist construction. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 He dropped in at a military lecture room to acquaint himself with the unit's performance of duty and training. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 He advanced important tasks which would serve as guidelines in increasing the unit's combat capability in every way, greatly pleased to learn that the officers and men of the unit are reliably standing guard over the defence line of the country, firmly armed with the Juche-oriented combat methods of the WPK. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 He learned in detail about the political work conducted among its servicepersons, going round the servicepersons' hall and entertainment facilities. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 He said the revolutionary comradeship of the KPA in which the officers and men share life and death is a source of matchless strength which no sophisticated weapons can ever overpower, saying it is very gratifying to see the officers and men of the unit creditably performing their duties united in thinking and purpose under the slogan of "Let the whole army become comrades!"  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 He took deep care of the service and living of the servicepersons, looking round an educational room, bedroom, mess hall, washroom, subsidiary food store, barber's and other places. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Watching photos of servicepersons displayed on the billboard for the honored, he said that they represented well the days of soldiers holding arms in hands. He urged all the servicepersons to glorify the days of their worthwhile military service with feats to become heroes of the 21st century. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 He acquainted himself with how "day for soldiers" is observed. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Noting that the "day for soldiers" briskly observed at all units is displaying ever-growing vitality, he added this noble trait can be found only in the People's Army in which superiors and inferiors are united close on the basis of kindred feelings. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 He gave servicepersons of the unit an automatic rifle as a gift and had a photo session with them. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 He was accompanied by KPA Generals Ri Myong Su, Hyon Chol Hae and Pak Jae Gyong.
